title: Need A Ride - Josh Kerr #LIVEARNETTE
description: One of the innovators of current day Surfing, Arnette team member Josh Kerr tells us about one of the heaviest moments of his life. He tells a tale of an epic day that almost went horribly wrong, and how it changed his life. See more of the #LIVEARNETTE video series here. Share your story #LIVEARNETTE.
